<para style="p">For the chief musician. A maschil of the sons of Korah.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />As the deer pants after streams of water,</para>

<para style="q1">so I thirst for you, God.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />I thirst for God, for the living God,</para>

<para style="q1">when will I come and appear before God?</para>
